show folders in server: type "nautilus" on terminal

%

setting up environment variables

open terminal

gedit .bashrc

export [variable name]=[name of folder] -- this creates variable that says where to 'cd' to
in terminal, use "cd $[variable name]"

test variable: type "echo [variable name]" on terminal

%

Git

to commit and use mesagem in less annoying way
git commit -m "put message here"


%

Stata

set more off
this makes the annoying thing that stata has that you have to keep pressing "more" to show results
set matsize increases the number of lines that stata shows

helpful for debugging in stata
set trace on

break lines ///
